subtitle: 20 million years in the past, survivors from the Lyran system,
who once rejected technological progress, evolved over eons on various planets. Their
apprehension about technology waned, enabling them to colonize and traverse distant stars,
and to finally battle on the same playing field as the draconians.
Initiating a fresh migratory wave, these feline humanoids were astounded to unearth burgeoning
different civilizations around them. Lost to ancient lore, their shared ancestry became
obscured, making each encounter with other species and worlds seem like a novel discovery. Yet,
these were merely their kin, sprouted from the same Lyran seeds back on Avyon. Over epochs,
varied evolutionary paths, interbreeding and genetic interventions rendered a mosaic of
various races of humanoids, each distinguished by size, complexion, and consciousness.
In this vast expanse, the omnipresent Draco and their eminent Ciakar leaders influenced
numerous races including the grays of Zeti Reticuli. Notably, certain humanoids in Orion,
majorly the Avyon genotype from Vega known as the Ahel Pleiadeans, found consonance with the
Ciakar's expansive pursuits, culminating in the formation of the Orion Empire.
The tensions and disagreements between the Federation and the Empire were in the many.
The early war were initially over territory, but it became a war of mind-sets and ideologies
and many were prejudice against other races of who were under either side.
On the one hand there was a group of human hybrid races that had joined forces in the
Federation. Many of its members recalled well their subjugation at the hands of the
Draco empire, and therefore rejected the ideas of colonization and intervention in
other worlds. They became committed to the idea of service-to-others.
The philosophy of service-to-self began innocently enough in the minds of its adopters. It proposed
that if everyone prioritized their own needs, the collective would naturally be cared for,
which sounded promising. However, what ensued was a paradigm where service-to-self came at
the expense of others, perpetuating the familiar cycle of victim and oppressor on our own planet.
This struggle between The Federation and The Empire became known as the Orion Wars
named such because most of the fighting took place in and around the Orion system. The war
lasted for millennia's and while there were truces and times of greater peace
the general trend was one of conflict and countless generations that grew up with war,
death, slavery, desperation and strife as the normal.
For hundreds of millennia, the conflicts within the Orion constellation wreaked
havoc on numerous life-bearing planets. It was often remarked that the night skies were
perpetually illuminated by stellar explosions, visible to the planet's dwellers. Over time,
a multitude of inhabitants chose to flee, seeking refuge from the looming threat of
subjugation or annihilation by the empire. Such dire circumstances led to the fracturing
of families, and numerous species inclined to resist the empire faced brutal extermination,
an atrocity paralleling the genocide inflicted upon the Jewish population on Earth. Furthermore,
planetary detention facilities were established to incarcerate species and
races that were less technologically advanced and had no strength to fight the empire.
Roughly, 12 million years ago,
In the constellation of Sirius the galactic federation held council.
One group of lyran humanoid refugees had found a new solar system and settled
on a evolved planet first called Maldek and later known as Tiamat.
But wherever these refugees went, the draconians and the wars kept coming closer.
The Sirian Lyrans initially did not want to get involved, but tensions were rising,
and soon occasional fights erupted between the different factions of refugees,
as to which course of action would be best.
The worlds of Sirius were mainly inhabited by refugees, reptilian,
lyran and mammalian crossbreeds who had fled the ceaseless wars and battered planets in
Orion to find peace and solace. It was there the Sirian Solution was established. This solution
would be the Origins of the Anunnaki royals and later Atlanteans of Nibiru.
In order to find peace, one of the federations proposed a creative plan for conflict resolution.
Inspired by the idea of an alchemical union of opposites, they suggested to the Empire and the
Federation a marriage between royal lineages to create a common ruling dynasty, mixing the
genetics of humanoid members of the Orion Royalty reptilian humanoid princess named Tiamat with a
high-ranking royal blood member of the Federation, a lyran prince humanoid man named Tybarian.
The strategy of blending lineages through marriage and crossbreeding was initiated,
leading to the emergence of a new royal hybrid lineage. This lineage was characterized by its
muscular, towering stature, elongated skulls, and skin tones that ranged from
very pale (albino) to shades of dark blue or red, embodying a warrior-like humanoid form.
These hybrids are recognized in historical records as the Anunnaki or, subsequently,
the Atlanteans, revered as the divine beings of ancient civilizations such as Mesopotamia,
Greece, Africa, India, Rome, Atlantis, and as depicted in the Old Testament.
Unfortunately, the “marriage” and subsequent new royal lineage did not have the result that
the Sirians and the federation had hoped for. Because of their different heritages they were
a race divided amongst themselves almost from the start, and it would prove difficult for the
Anunnaki royals to unite as one family, or to hold to one set of principles for all the galaxies.
Also, many races refused to pledge their allegiance to the new dynasty,
because they disagreed with any genetic manipulation that included reptilian DNA.
However, this union did create a peace that lasted for a few hundred thousand years,
with the Anunnaki royals ruling, before warfare once again exploded throughout the Galaxy.
Subsequently, the situation of the Orion Wars transformed with the birth of a remarkable child
in Sirius. This child, was believed to be the inaugural incarnation of Christ Consciousness
in our realm and sent by Yaweh, later recognized in future epochs and many myths as Merlin, wielded
fifth-density capabilities and seventh-density abilities, manifesting as "miracles". Prophecies
foretold that this being would have the power to incarnate at will, with a soul so powerful
it could transcend space-time. As an adult, this being possessed the ability to resurrect the dead
and create planets and galaxies with merely thoughts. Propagating teachings echoing later
peaceful luminaries like Yeshua or Buddha, Merlin advocated unconditional love and forgiveness,
eventually dissolving entrenched dualistic perceptions, which led to a truce between the
empire and federation. This newfound understanding heralded an ascension in collective consciousness,
culminating in the elevation of vast populations into higher densities.
Under this newfound peace, the Orion Empire metamorphosed into a matriarchy,
with the reptilian royal queen named Tiamat, the Dragon Queen, at its helm. She was given
the luscious planet Maldek as a gift from her husband Tybarian, where they proclaimed the
planet to be named after her. With long eons of peace, the 13 new humanoid-reptilian hybrid
families that sprouted from Tiamat & Tybarian, persisted in the ancient reptilian ways,
which can be found in The Enuma Elish. These families, ancestors to the present-day Cabal
or the 13 Royal Bloodlines, sought only for self service and dominion over resources and power.
The Draco Fleet, driven by an unending quest for new planets for farming and
mining to sustain their race and uphold their vast infrastructure,
was in a perpetual state of expansion and movement.
Approximately 365 million years ago, two Draco reptilian brothers, aboard a scout ship of
their Reptilian Fleet discovered that Tiamat the planet was missing a tidal system necessary for
accelerating life's evolution. To address this, the Ciakar empire introduced a strategically
positioned hollowed-out planetoid, now known as the Moon. Moon, enigmatic observations multiply.
Puzzling aspects include its disproportionate size compared to Tiamat later known as Earth,
surprisingly light weight, mathematically precise placement relative to Earth and the Sun,
and synchronized rotation, always revealing the same face. Additionally, modern Astro physicists
have found evidence that suggests the Moon is hollow with metallic properties beneath its
surface. Anomalies on the Moon have been reported by past astronomers, including figures like Plato
and Sir William Herschel, for centuries. Considering the Moon as an artificially
constructed planetoid satellite which aligns with Occam's Razor, simplifying these mysteries.
Presently, the Moon served as a command hub for the Milky Way segment, a neutral
zone inhabited by representatives of various civilizations of the Empire and Annunaki of
Atlantis. It also hosts the system broadcasting the artificial 3rd Density Matrix to the planet.
300 million years ago The Draconian queen Tiamat created breeding strategies on her planet and
evolutionary forces led to the appearance of the first reptiles on Tiamat or Earth.
252 million years ago As Tiamat or Earth oxygen levels rose,
making it less suitable for the Draco, they intervened with an asteroid impact to elevate
CO2 levels and eliminate weaker species, paving the way for dinosaur dominance.
227 million years ago Dinosaurs proliferated, with carnivorous species vital for crossbreeding
Draco soldiers and herbivores left to grow as a potential protein source.
200 million years ago To combat rising oxygen levels, the Ciakar orchestrated
another asteroid impact, targeting burgeoning mammalian species competing with dinosaurs.
Then, interstellar involvements took center stage, with the Paa Tal, an Ancient Builder Race,
establishing a base in modern-day Antarctica in response to continuous Draco interventions.
Many intergalactic civilizations were flourishing. Trade and exploration connected
systems like Orion, Sirius, parts of Lyra, Draco, Vega, and the Pleiades. This attracted
various civilizations to our solar system, leading to confrontations with the Draco.
Primitive civilizations in Lyra, and other unaware races,
remained undisturbed by more advanced entities, adhering to non-intervention policies. However,
some reptilian factions, devoid of such principles,
took control of these civilizations, enslaving and conducting genetic experiments on them.
Over time, a myriad of breeds emerged due to the Draco's genetic programs and the natural
evolutionary processes. The universe saw a plethora of races like Humans,
Reptilians, Canines, Avians, Felines, Amphibians, Insectoids, and more. Some
advanced races even transcended physical forms, existing as pure Love/Light unions.
Reptilian races predominantly inhabited Draco, Orion, Sirius,
and various colonies across the universe, including Tiamat or Earth where the
reptilians genetically created and engineered Dinosaurs. Some reptilians evolved spiritually
and developed positive affiliations. Particularly, some from the Alpha
Draconian branch achieved a 5D vibrational state, harmonizing with other 5D races.
From 200 million to 22 million years ago, the universe witnessed a generally
harmonious evolution interspersed with occasional conflicts and upheavals.
Initially the reptilians began settling on Mars, where they soon faced sanctification by the local
civilizations due to their malevolent disposition. It was during this time of peace throughout the
Universe that the being known as Merlin had the idea to create a system of “Living Libraries”
planets that contain flora and fauna from hundreds of other worlds to act as a kind of storehouse for
genetic material from lost worlds. Earth which was once Tiamat, was already quite diverse,
and was one of the 12 planets in the Galaxy selected to act as Living Library or store
house. It was then thousands of races also journeyed here under the protection and rule of
Queen Tiamat from all over to seed different plant and animal species – octopus, mushrooms, orchids,
lions and canines etc. Many of them stayed for a while, delighting in the rich lushness of Tiamat.
The dragon queen Tiamat herself helped seed life and created a giant, androgynous, humanoid race,
called the Namlu’u, to act as guardians of the Living Library on Tiamat which would one day
be a piece of planet earth. The Namlu’u were the race that the ancient Greeks called the Titans.
The giants that were the “parents” of the “gods” — meaning a race of 50 to 60 foot tall humanoids
who existed here before the Annunaki arrived. This Era of peace and harmony would last throughout the
Galaxy for approximately 5.5 Million years, until the next great war known as The War in Heaven.
A group of 15 royal bloodlines from Orion, known for their dark and violent history, took refuge on
Maldek, exacerbating the planet's decline. These beings, possessing powerful multi-dimensional
capabilities and various avatars, influenced Maldek's inhabitants—descendants of a defeated
reptoid lineage from Earth—towards self-serving ideals, technological reliance, and control,
further spiraling the planet into decay. This shift towards aggression led to threats against
peaceful Martians, escalating to demands for Mars to surrender its territory or face conquest.
The conflict drew in aid from the Pleiadians, summoned by Martian appeals, which Maldek
interpreted as provocation, leading to a violent clash. Maldek used advanced
electromagnetic-gravitic technology against Mars, deploying toxic chemical bombs that devastated the
Martian atmosphere and population, with survivors fleeing to Sirius, the Pleiades, or Earth.
In retaliation, the Pleiadians attacked Maldek, causing its leaders to disastrously increase
their energy grid's power. This action led to Maldek's destruction, forming the asteroid belt
between Mars and Jupiter, and fragmenting the souls of its inhabitants. These soul fragments,
along with those of the Martians, sought refuge on Earth, joining its diverse soul population.
Before Maldek's destruction, the 15 Orion leaders escaped to Atlantis, 52,000 years in the past,
intending to influence Earth's history. However, the Pleiadians countered by
imposing a 3rd Density Matrix to trap the Orion group and stabilize the situation,
integrating the traumatized souls from Maldek and Mars into Earth's reincarnation cycle.
These events have shaped Earth's history, with the Orion group merging with other
influential factions to form what is known as the Cabal, while some
Pleiadians work towards assisting Earth's evolution beyond the 3rd Density Matrix.
Sanat Kumara, leading a group from Venus, established the 5D city of Shamballa above
the Gobi Sea to stabilize Earth's situation, later creating a 4D city beneath it. Working
with Pleiadians and evolved Martians, they aided the traumatized souls from the Maldek-Mars war,
incarnating as primitive hominids with reduced psychic abilities.
The group of humans from the Pleiades who had settled here about 17.5 Million years before, and
who were also living at the 4th Density (most of Agartha is 4D territory) had already established
a city underground and they welcomed the Nacaals and also assisted with the construction.
Then the Nacaals began. Together with the Pleiadian group and the more highly evolved
Martians who had escaped the destruction of their planet’s atmosphere in their light bodies,
they began helping the traumatized souls of all those who had perished in the Maldek/Mars war, who
were hovering around Tiamat later known as earth in a great cloud, waiting to incarnate here.
These poor souls were so traumatized and fragmented. They had lost all their psychic
abilities and Akashic memory and were barely sentient. They incarnated into
the 3rd Density Matrix as primitive hominids, the genus we know as Homo Habilis. The active
DNA was reduced to 2 strands, with the 10 other strands existing only as potential.
The different soul families (each of which was comprised of shards from a previously intact,
single soul) incarnated into different tribes. Essentially,
one tribe = one soul family = one shattered Maldekian or Martian soul.
To this day, many of the souls who inhabit current Earth are from this group and while
some have evolved and healed over time, regaining much of their former spiritual prowess, others
have not and are still barely above their ancient hominid ancestors in terms of consciousness.
The reason that our fossil record shows so many different species of the genus
Homo subsequently appearing and disappearing throughout the millions of years that follow
this time is because of both evolution and continued genetic manipulation by the
Nacaals and Atlanteans of Nibiru, as well as many other groups like pleiadians.
In fact, descendants from these tribes would eventually be altered
into Homo Sapiens by the Annunaki about 2 million
years after the introduction of Homo Habilis, Homo erectus and Denisovans.
